## Setup

```sh
mix deps.get
{{#if (eq elixirOrm "ecto-sql")}}
mix ecto.setup
{{/if}}
{{#if (ne elixirWebFramework "none")}}
mix phx.server
{{else}}
iex -S mix
{{/if}}
```

{{#if (ne elixirWebFramework "none")}}
Open http://localhost:4000.
{{/if}}

For tests:

```sh
mix test
```

{{#if (eq elixirDeploy "fly")}}
## Fly.io

```sh
fly launch --copy-config
fly secrets set SECRET_KEY_BASE="$(mix phx.gen.secret)"
fly deploy
```
{{/if}}

{{#if (eq elixirDeploy "gigalixir")}}
## Gigalixir

```sh
gigalixir create
gigalixir config:set SECRET_KEY_BASE="$(mix phx.gen.secret)"
git push gigalixir main
```
{{/if}}

