{{#if (eq elixirAuth "guardian")}}
## Guardian auth

Guardian token endpoints are available at `/api/auth/token` and `/api/auth/me`. Set `GUARDIAN_SECRET_KEY` before deploying.
{{/if}}

{{#if (eq elixirAuth "ueberauth")}}
## Ueberauth

Add provider strategy packages and entries under `config :ueberauth, Ueberauth, providers: [...]` before using `/auth/:provider`.
{{/if}}
